<li class='cover' id='bookCover_1051513'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1051513.Charlie_and_the_Chocolate_Factory"><img alt="Charlie and the Chocolate Factory" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348470694l/1051513._SX98_.jpg" />
